	{
		id
		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked

		createdAt

query ($id:ID)
{
	oAuthFindAccessTokenById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:OAuthUpdateAccessTokenInput!)
{
	oAuthUpdateAccessToken (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	oAuthDeleteAccessTokenById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthDeleteAccessTokens (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
